::Proto::

Proto stops by a door, pressing a button on the controlls. The door opens, 
revealing a room, large enough for two bots.

"You two can be in here," Proto says, indicating Airbomber and Infectra with 
his arm. He looks at Stranato. "The solo quarters are further down the hall," 
he says, walking off again. He stops at a door, opening it to a smaller room 
than the first.

"You can use this one."
